{"id": "1508506821361537291", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "在稍後講解打法的時候 會補上最新研究跟最高傷害的搭配", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:27:32.914000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508506878542610433", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "#  配置", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:27:46.547000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508507008104661223", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "混沌24隊需要高額精通跟強力回銀角", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:28:17.437000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508507091654938724", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "精通至少要大概400", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:28:37.357000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508507599824490667", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "有融朵或是子宮(慈悲的哺育) 可以稍微降低一下要求", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:30:38.514000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508508053144604805", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "隊伍綁定環拉\n需要其更改鑰令的能力\n其他隊友建議選擇塔薇 或 融朵\n可以兩個都上 也可以搭配萊克或是哈姆林", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:32:26.594000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508508406489546792", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "我個人是比較喜歡搭配塔薇 哈姆林的\n塔薇相對融朵可以更穩定提供強效 有高額回銀能力 而且自帶兩個鑰令", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:33:50.838000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508508523598975006", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "哈姆林則是幫忙過牌跟減少算力消耗", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:34:18.759000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508508713600811098", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "#  命輪的選擇", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:35:04.059000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508509334240362659", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "24:\n優先考慮+12星天之獸\n其次可以根據關卡的長短考慮24專(畸體回噬)或是杜勒專(安息之吻)", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:37:32.031000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508509589388263505", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "關卡短的\n比如說3 4上24專\n關卡長的就杜勒專(因為要收頭成長)", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:38:32.863000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508509871648149574", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "銀鑰位:\n建議是可以雙持一張+12銀鑰屬性的", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:39:40.159000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508509993391886357", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "其他隊友:\n需要補充精通以及帶櫻花下的迷思", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:40:09.185000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508510417066918009", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "那高傷害的選擇可以攜帶皮克曼專(寫實主義悖謬)以及紅茶(私密午歇時間)", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:41:50.197000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508510613876510913", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "#  密契及鑰令", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:42:37.120000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508510875747881001", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "24建議猩紅之悸補充爆擊率\n銀鑰位建議生機榨取", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:43:39.555000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
{"id": "1508511015019614441", "channel_id": "1508505837923209396", "author_id": "806384001895890965", "author_name": "0.0._.0_0.", "content": "其他隊友帶高精通的\n(我個人是選擇精通拼盤\n海歸線拼詛咒兔)", "timestamp": "2026-05-25T16:44:12.760000+00:00", "thread_id": "1508505837923209396"}
